data.description: Motivated Seller! Needs a little work on cooors but great value! Large 5 or 6 bedroom with Gourmet custom kitchen on large wooded lot in Magnolia! Custom Kitchen, 2 custom showers! Oversized Primary Suite, Guest house/Cabana  (no bath) in back of property. 2 car attached garage. Quick access to 1488, great schools, community pool, recreation area, park with small lake in walking distance, LOW TAXES!
